fields.value: Urban Mass Transportation Administration Financial and Operating Data, 1981

dsDescriptionValue.value: This database is an on-going series of information on planning by public transit systems, Federal, state, and local governments, and the public. For the public sector, it provides information on investment decisions, by all levels of government. It is a unique resource for public transit management, planning, policy-making, and other analytical applications.
